28:37.977 --> 28:40.240
Dr. McCabe?

28:40.283 --> 28:41.763
Dr. McCabe.

28:41.807 --> 28:43.547
Detectives Reagan and Baez.

28:43.591 --> 28:44.548
Yes?

28:44.592 --> 28:45.767
You are Dr. McCabe, right?

28:45.811 --> 28:47.551
Camille McCabe, PhD.

28:47.595 --> 28:48.857
Mm. So not

28:48.901 --> 28:52.339
Dr. Camille McCabe,
couples therapist, right?

28:52.382 --> 28:54.602
Can I help you detectives
with something?

28:54.645 --> 28:55.777
Yeah, actually,
you can.

28:55.821 --> 28:57.300
How long have
you known Richard Hayes?

28:57.344 --> 28:58.649
Who?

28:58.693 --> 29:00.086
DANNY: The guy with
his tongue down your throat.

29:01.435 --> 29:02.392
CAMILLE:
I don't know.

29:02.436 --> 29:04.177
Uh, a year?

29:04.220 --> 29:06.527
And how long have you
and Richard Hayes

29:06.570 --> 29:08.529
been gaslighting Mrs. Hayes?

29:08.572 --> 29:09.748
E

29:11.227 --> 29:12.838
We had been seeing each other

29:12.881 --> 29:14.753
