when we first discussed it.

29:14.796 --> 29:18.408
Discuss your plan to gaslight
Richard's wife Clara.

29:20.671 --> 29:22.064
Richard tried

29:22.108 --> 29:24.240
to leave her many times.
She would simply refuse.

29:24.284 --> 29:27.461
And that's why you decided
to drive her mad?

29:27.504 --> 29:30.812
It doesn't make you insane,
it just confuses you.

29:30.856 --> 29:32.509
Whose idea was it?

29:32.553 --> 29:34.381
I was doing
some research on the topic

29:34.424 --> 29:36.775
for one of my lectures,
and it caught Richard's eye.

29:36.818 --> 29:38.646
He asked me to
drill down on it.

29:38.689 --> 29:39.821
And you did.

29:39.865 --> 29:41.518
DANNY: And when
that didn't work,

29:41.562 --> 29:44.521
you decided to double down,
and take on the role

29:44.565 --> 29:47.568
of a phony couples therapist
for Richard and Clara?

29:47.611 --> 29:48.874
Richard insisted
she was close to breaking.

29:50.136 --> 29:51.659
He just thought she needed
a little nudge.

29:51.702 --> 29:53.661
"Nudge" being drugging her
with chloroform

29:53.704 --> 29:55.794
and staging an attempted murder.

29:55.837 --> 29:57.186
Hey, that was all Richard.

29:57.230 --> 29:58.753
I had nothing to do with that.

29:58.797 --> 30:01.147
When I found out the reason
that Richard wanted me

30:01.190 --> 30:02.496
to research the effects
of chloroform,

30:02.539 --> 30:04.019
I told him he was crazy.

30:04.063 --> 30:06.065
I said I wanted nothing
to do with it.

30:06.108 --> 30:08.458
But you didn't call the police.

30:08.502 --> 30:10.591
No.

30:10.634 --> 30:12.506
But I should have.

30:12.549 --> 30:14.725
I absolutely should have.

30:14.769 --> 30:16.858
Would you be willing
to testify in court

30:16.902 --> 30:18.164
to all of this?

30:19.556 --> 30:22.603
Absolutely.
A hundred percent.

30:23.996 --> 30:26.520
Richard should pay
for what he did.

30:39.794 --> 30:40.664
CAMILLE :
Absolutely.

30:40.708 --> 30:43.363
A hundred percent.

30:43.406 --> 30:44.843
Richard should pay
for what he did.

30:48.194 --> 30:51.414
This is garbage.
Complete and utter nonsense.

30:51.458 --> 30:52.633
This was all her idea.

30:52.676 --> 30:54.504
He said, she said.DANNY:
Yep.

30:54.548 --> 30:56.158
And she said first,
so guess what?

30:56.202 --> 30:57.507
She's the grand
prize winner.

30:57.551 --> 30:59.118
Well, she's lying.
Mm.

30:59.161 --> 31:00.771
It was her idea
to fake the shooting.

31:00.815 --> 31:01.685
Her idea to
make it look like

31:01.729 --> 31:04.601
Clara shot me.I'm sure it was.

31:04.645 --> 31:06.647
I'm not lying.
This was all her plan.

31:07.691 --> 31:08.649
She was there, too.

31:08.692 --> 31:11.695
Say again.It's true.

31:11.739 --> 31:14.481
She was in the kitchen,
hiding.

31:14.524 --> 31:16.657
She's the one that slipped
chloroform into her drink.

31:16.700 --> 31:17.571
Hell, she's the one
who actually shot me

31:17.614 --> 31:19.051
after Clara passed out.

31:19.094 --> 31:21.401
Sounds like you're throwing
a little bit of a Hail Mary,

31:21.444 --> 31:22.619
don't you think, Richard?

31:22.663 --> 31:23.794
It's the God's honest truth.

31:23.838 --> 31:25.622
He said, she said.
Yeah.

31:25.666 --> 31:27.668
Only matters what
you can prove. Come on.

31:27.711 --> 31:29.670
Come on, get up.Wait, wait, wait.

31:29.713 --> 31:32.151
I can prove it.
I can.

31:32.194 --> 31:33.717
How you gonna
do that, Richard?

31:33.761 --> 31:36.720
You gonna gaslight us, too?No, no, no.

31:36.764 --> 31:38.679
I've got a nanny cam
in the living room.

31:38.722 --> 31:41.160
I put it there to keep an eye
on Clara when I wasn't home.

31:41.203 --> 31:43.249
Camille didn't know
about it, but...

31:43.292 --> 31:45.686
it had to have
recorded everything.

31:45.729 --> 31:46.905
The shooting will be on there.

31:46.948 --> 31:48.907
Hmm. Right.

32:05.880 --> 32:08.970
Oh...
RICHARD:
See?

32:09.014 --> 32:10.711
Told ya.

32:17.196 --> 32:21.678
Well, you guys are crazy,
but this is good news.

32:21.722 --> 32:23.767
Yeah?Yeah.

32:23.811 --> 32:26.683
Does this get me off?It gets your wife off.

32:26.727 --> 32:27.902
And puts you
and your girlfriend away

32:27.946 --> 32:28.990
for a very long time.

32:29.034 --> 32:31.514
Come on, get up.
Get up!

33:05.766 --> 33:07.028
Officers, fall in
for roll call.

33:11.772 --> 33:13.687
Officer Cooper.Here, sir.

33:13.730 --> 33:16.298
2-9 Frank. Don't forget
to fill up this time.

33:16.342 --> 33:18.039
Officer Tedesco.Here.

33:18.083 --> 33:19.127
Patrol post 15.

33:19.171 --> 33:22.130
Officer Janko.Present, sir.

33:22.174 --> 33:23.349
Patrol post 11.

33:23.392 --> 33:24.437
Yes, sir.

33:24.480 --> 33:26.656
And welcome to the 2-9.

33:26.700 --> 33:28.876
Officer Goldman...Yes, sir.

33:28.919 --> 33:30.921
Patrol post 9...

33:47.808 --> 33:51.812
Hey, Erin, I'm so sorry.

33:51.855 --> 33:53.074
No, it's me.

33:53.118 --> 33:55.076
It's just, it's this job.
I should have...

33:55.120 --> 33:57.209
Nonsense. I should have
just kept my mouth shut.

33:57.252 --> 33:59.080
And I should have listened.

33:59.124 --> 34:00.125
What do you say
we bury the hatchet

34:00.168 --> 34:01.430
in a couple of martinis?

34:01.474 --> 34:04.607
Straight up with a twist?Let's do it.

34:11.832 --> 34:13.834
