indistinct chatter]

34:19.187 --> 34:20.841
Good night.

34:20.884 --> 34:22.886
WOMAN:
Bye.

34:30.155 --> 34:31.591
Deputy Commissioner Moore,
come with us, please.

34:31.634 --> 34:33.071
What the hell?!

34:33.114 --> 34:35.986
Just come with us, sir.
It's okay.

34:36.030 --> 34:37.988
Come with us, right now,
let's go.

35:01.316 --> 35:04.798
12 minutes and four seconds
from pickup.

35:04.841 --> 35:07.148
Well done.

35:07.192 --> 35:08.671
That'll be all,
Inspector,

35:08.715 --> 35:09.716
and thank you.

35:12.936 --> 35:15.069
Where am I?

35:15.113 --> 35:18.072
Bravo Bunker.

35:19.856 --> 35:22.729
This place was created
in the wake of 911.

35:22.772 --> 35:24.470
Why am I here?

35:24.513 --> 35:26.820
We've been asking ourselves
the same thing.

35:26.863 --> 35:28.517
Yeah, boss.

35:28.561 --> 35:30.606
I am getting to that.

35:32.260 --> 35:36.177
Look, I was assuming
that all three of you

35:36.221 --> 35:40.790
would be in my office
at the same time.

35:42.966 --> 35:45.969
You were delayed, so you were
deleted from the drill.

35:46.013 --> 35:47.884
Yeah, I felt pretty deleted.

35:47.928 --> 35:50.713
I-- You made that very clear.

35:51.932 --> 35:54.717
But there wasn't an option.

35:54.761 --> 35:58.547
No one talks of this place
outside of this place.

36:00.549 --> 36:04.292
This facility was designed
for only the most

36:04.336 --> 36:08.209
indispensable men and women
of the NYPD.

36:12.909 --> 36:16.870
I have come to realize
that title and rank

36:16.913 --> 36:21.570
are not the only things
that go into "indispensable."

36:23.442 --> 36:25.139
You are.

36:28.969 --> 36:30.710
You are.

36:45.942 --> 36:47.944
You are.

37:01.523 --> 37:03.699
I will now show you your bunks

37:03.743 --> 37:06.572
and the kitchen

37:06.615 --> 37:08.791
while you say a prayer

37:08.835 --> 37:11.403
that we never have
to use them.

37:11.446 --> 37:12.621
EDDIE:
In the name of the Father,

37:12.665 --> 37:14.406
the Son, and the Holy Spirit.

37:14.449 --> 37:18.192
Our Father, full of grace
who arts in heaven,

37:18.236 --> 37:21.456
