37:23.763 --> 37:24.851
HENRY:
Okay, Eddie, Eddie,

37:24.894 --> 37:26.896
I have to stop you there.

37:26.940 --> 37:28.811
Seriously, what was that?

37:28.855 --> 37:30.335
I was saying grace.

37:30.378 --> 37:31.640
I have no idea what
you were just saying.

37:31.684 --> 37:33.294
Yeah, but it definitely
wasn't grace.

37:33.338 --> 37:34.600
JAMIE:
It's okay, babe,

37:34.643 --> 37:36.079
I think you just got
a little confused.

37:36.123 --> 37:38.038
I think you were saying
the Our Father...

37:38.081 --> 37:39.648
With a little Hail Mary
thrown in there.

37:39.692 --> 37:41.302
And then she circled back
to the Our Father again.Right...

37:41.346 --> 37:45.088
SEAN: And then it was just kind
of like a super weird mash-up.

37:45.132 --> 37:46.351
It made no sense.

37:46.394 --> 37:48.266
It's okay, babe.
They're just busting chops.

37:48.309 --> 37:50.268
Yeah, it's-- I just--
I was just, I don't know,

37:50.311 --> 37:52.966
I was just trying
to fit in. I...

37:53.009 --> 37:55.795
I don't know why you guys
have to all be so mean.

37:55.838 --> 37:56.883
Eddie, they were--

37:56.926 --> 37:58.319
You just sat there.
You let them.

38:04.282 --> 38:05.413
Really, guys?

38:05.457 --> 38:06.762
Jamie...

38:10.549 --> 38:13.856
Well... happy?

38:15.380 --> 38:17.469
Who knew she was so sensitive?

38:17.512 --> 38:19.297
Who knew we were
so insensitive?

38:19.340 --> 38:21.690
I guess we're just
used to each other.

38:21.734 --> 38:24.345
I started it.
I guess I'll go and apologize.

38:24.389 --> 38:27.435
Thanks, guys, I really
appreciate the warm welcome.

38:27.479 --> 38:28.828
What's next, noogies?

38:28.871 --> 38:29.829
She leave?No.

38:29.872 --> 38:32.353
She's just getting a grip.

38:32.397 --> 38:35.225
Eddie, I-I started it.
It was wrong.

38:35.269 --> 38:36.488
It was just wrong.

38:36.531 --> 38:38.316
Yeah, I think it was
just our family's

38:38.359 --> 38:40.840
poor attempt at humor.
We're-We're sorry, Eddie.

38:40.883 --> 38:43.321
Lame of us to go
for the easy joke.

38:43.364 --> 38:44.583
Even lamer of us

38:44.626 --> 38:46.193
to make fun of
the effort you put in.

38:49.022 --> 38:50.806
Sorry.
Sorry.

38:50.850 --> 38:53.113
Sorry.

38:53.156 --> 38:55.376
I don't know.

