39:15.309 --> 39:16.397
Payback is a bitch.

39:16.441 --> 39:18.312
Oh, so you were
in on it?

39:18.356 --> 39:19.618
Well, after last week's
initiation,

39:19.661 --> 39:20.706
I told him I wanted
to give you guys

39:20.749 --> 39:21.837
